  "body": "Is there a way to disable TLS session tickets? The Envoy docs and other sources[1][2] mention security considerations and risks for using session tickets, and we don't need session resumption at all so we'd like to not be exposed to any possible risks.\r\n\r\n[1] https://www.imperialviolet.org/2013/06/27/botchingpfs.html, also mentioned in the Envoy docs.\r\n[2] https://blog.filippo.io/we-need-to-talk-about-session-tickets/",
